{
  "stem": "9558.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he came out and he pulled out his sabre.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they all ran away, because once you start up with a soldier, he was allowed to kill you.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You're not allowed to touch a soldier.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had plenty-- plenty of incidents there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What do you mean by change?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my sister was married--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--about that time.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Two sisters were married before the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one sister moved away to a small town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- [NON-ENGLISH] it was called.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her husband came from there, and they had some kind of little farm.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so it was a little bit easier.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Used to go and buy some-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] --jackets or pants, and go out there and exchange by the Polacks, because you couldn't buy anything to wear, for flour, or for butter, or potatoes.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this is how we survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then my third sister married.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was a beautiful girl, and she married a guy from our town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "His name was Shlomo Pincusfeld.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before the war.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were very well off, so she helped us a lot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So between the two sisters, when they took my older brother right away to work, and I used to go around and exchange stuff to have food.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That how we were interested, because we had the house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We lived in the house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And should be able to bring some potatoes and bread.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's what you prayed for.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If you had potatoes and bread, you had everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And this is how we lived till 1942. 1942, they made Judenrein.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And we had to leave our houses and everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother went to my sister in that small town there.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
